OL,3,CDeaths were avoidable in deadliest
OL,4,CChannel crossing, inquiry finds
OL,6,FWords by ITV News producer Eva Carroll
OL,8,FAn inquiry into the deadliest Channel
OL,9,Fcrossing on record has concluded that
OL,10,Fthe loss of life was avoidable.
OL,12,FThe Cranston Inquiry found systemic
OL,13,Ffailures, missed opportunities, and
OL,14,Finadequate resourcing undermined the
OL,15,FUK's maritime search and rescue
OL,16,Fresponse on the night of the tragedy.
OL,18,FAt least 27 people - men, women and
OL,19,Fchildren - drowned when their dinghy
OL,20,Fcapsized one night in November 2021.
