OL,6,FFour are still missing, and just two
OL,7,Fsurvived. The survivors were
OL,8,Fdiscovered in French waters nearly 12
OL,9,Fhours after the first calls for help.
OL,11,FMore people could have survived the
OL,12,Ftragedy, the inquiry suggests, if HM
OL,13,FCoastguard's search and rescue efforts
OL,14,Fhad continued in daylight hours.
OL,16,FSome individuals were likely still
OL,17,Falive at sunrise, and a smaller number
OL,18,Fmay have even survived until the early
OL,19,Fafternoon.
