OL,3,CDeaths were avoidable in deadliest
OL,4,CChannel crossing, inquiry finds
OL,6,FThe report highlighted that calls,
OL,7,Fmessages, and WhatsApp geolocation
OL,8,Finformation from the small boat were
OL,9,Fmissed or not followed up on by HM
OL,10,FCoastguard.
OL,12,FThe independent probe, led by Sir Ross
OL,13,FCranston, was set up to find out the
OL,14,Ftruth of what happened.
OL,16,FAt the closing hearing, Sir Ross said:
OL,17,F"The practice of small boat crossings
OL,18,Fmust end. Apart from other reasons, it
OL,19,Fis imperative to prevent further loss
OL,20,Fof life.
