OL,6,F"Travelling on board a small,
OL,7,Funseaworthy, and overcrowded boat, and
OL,8,Fcrossing one of the busiest shipping
OL,9,Flanes in the world is an inherently
OL,10,Fdangerous activity."
OL,12,FSir Ross' report highlighted the
OL,13,Fprecarity of the vessel, which had
OL,14,Finadequate safety equipment and was
OL,15,Fdangerously overloaded.
OL,17,FA French naval vessel was closest to
OL,18,Fthe small boat but failed to respond
OL,19,Fto the Mayday alert.
