OL,6,FAlthough the report suggested that HM
OL,7,FCoastguard in Dover was in an
OL,8,F"intolerable position" with chronic
OL,9,Fstaff shortages and limited capacity,
OL,10,Fit also highlighted cultural issues.
OL,12,FThis includes the widely held belief
OL,13,Fwithin HM Coastguard that small-boat
OL,14,Fcallers "exaggerated distress", which
OL,15,Fled to the underestimation of the
OL,16,Femergency.
