OL,6,FFamilies told the inquiry of their
OL,7,Fdevastating and ongoing grief.
OL,9,FThe report recognises the dedication
OL,10,Fof HM Coastguard, Border Force teams,
OL,11,FRNLI and other voluntary lifeguards.
OL,13,FHowever, the inquiry stresses that
OL,14,Fsystemic change is needed to support
OL,15,Fand strengthen their efforts,
OL,16,Fproviding 18 recommendations designed
OL,17,Fto strengthen the UK's maritime search
OL,18,Fand rescue capability.
